{"schemaVersion":1,"bookId":"toefl-sentences","unitId":"sentence-004","title":"Sentence 04","sectionId":"sentences-001","sectionTitle":"Sentence 01-10","pageStart":36,"pageEnd":41,"extractionMethod":"text-layer","wordEntryCount":37,"duplicateEntryCount":0,"pages":[{"number":36,"blocks":[{"type":"title","text":"Sentence 04"},{"type":"text","text":"Of the millions who saw Haley’s Comet in 1986, how many people"},{"type":"text","text":"will live long enough to see it return in the twenty-first century."},{"type":"text","text":"1986年看见哈雷慧星的千百万人当中，有多少人能够长寿到足"},{"type":"text","text":"以目睹它在21世纪的回归呢？"},{"type":"section","text":"语法笔记"},{"type":"text","text":"本句的主干是How many people will live long enough to see it return"},{"type":"text","text":"in the twenty-first century。这句看似一个普通的疑问句，但实际上含有"},{"type":"text","text":"感叹句的功能。"},{"type":"section","text":"核心词表"},{"type":"entry","text":"comet /ˈkɑːmət/ n. 彗星","headword":"comet"},{"type":"note","text":"记忆 come（来）+t→很多年才来一次的星星→彗星"},{"type":"note","text":"同根 cometary a. 彗星的"},{"type":"text","text":"Halley’s Comet 哈雷彗星（以英国科学家哈雷的名字命名，公转周"},{"type":"text","text":"期是76年）"},{"type":"section","text":"主题归纳"},{"type":"text","text":"八大行星："},{"type":"entry","text":"Earth /ɜːrθ/ n. 地球","headword":"Earth"},{"type":"entry","text":"Jupiter /ˈdʒuːpɪtər/ n. 木星","headword":"Jupiter"}]},{"number":37,"blocks":[{"type":"note","text":"记忆 朱庇特（Jupiter）是罗马神话中的天神"},{"type":"entry","text":"Mars /mɑːrz/ n. 火星","headword":"Mars"},{"type":"note","text":"记忆 马尔斯（Mars）是罗马神话中的战神"},{"type":"entry","text":"Mercury /ˈmɜːrkjəri/ n. 水星","headword":"Mercury"},{"type":"note","text":"记忆 墨丘利（Mercury）罗马神话中天神Jupiter的儿子，担任诸神"},{"type":"text","text":"的使者"},{"type":"entry","text":"Neptune /ˈneptjuːn/ n. 海王星","headword":"Neptune"},{"type":"note","text":"记忆 涅普顿（Neptune）是罗马神话中的海神"},{"type":"entry","text":"Saturn /ˈsætɜːrn/ n. 土星","headword":"Saturn"},{"type":"note","text":"记忆 萨杜恩（Saturn）是罗马神话中的农业之神，排在Jupiter之"},{"type":"text","text":"后"},{"type":"entry","text":"Uranus /ˈjʊrənəs/ n. 天王星","headword":"Uranus"},{"type":"note","text":"记忆 乌拉诺斯（Uranus）是希腊神话中的天空之神"},{"type":"entry","text":"Venus /ˈviːnəs/ n. 金星","headword":"Venus"}]},{"number":38,"blocks":[{"type":"note","text":"记忆 维纳斯（Venus）是罗马神话中爱与美的女神"},{"type":"text","text":"常见星体："},{"type":"entry","text":"asteroid /ˈæstərɔɪd/ n. 小行星","headword":"asteroid"},{"type":"note","text":"记忆 aster（星星）+oid（形状）→小行星"},{"type":"text","text":"dwarf planet 矮行星"},{"type":"entry","text":"meteor /ˈmiːtiər/ n. 流星","headword":"meteor"},{"type":"note","text":"同根 meteoric a. 流星的"},{"type":"text","text":"meteor shower 流星雨"},{"type":"entry","text":"meteoroid /ˈmiːtɪəˌrɔɪd/ n. 流星体","headword":"meteoroid"}]},{"number":39,"blocks":[{"type":"note","text":"同根 meteor n. 流星"},{"type":"text","text":"natural satellite天然卫星"},{"type":"entry","text":"planet /ˈplænɪt/ n. 行星","headword":"planet"},{"type":"note","text":"同根 planetary a. 行星的"},{"type":"text","text":"planetoid n. 小行星"},{"type":"entry","text":"Pluto /ˈpluːtoʊ/ n. 冥王星","headword":"Pluto"},{"type":"entry","text":"quasar /ˈkweɪzɑːr/ n. 类星体","headword":"quasar"},{"type":"note","text":"记忆 qu＋a＋sar（看作star，星星）→类星体"},{"type":"entry","text":"satellite /ˈsætəlaɪt/ n. 卫星","headword":"satellite"},{"type":"note","text":"搭配 weather satellite 气象卫星"},{"type":"entry","text":"star /stɑːr/ n. 恒星","headword":"star"},{"type":"text","text":"terrestrial planet 类地行星"},{"type":"text","text":"与“天体运转”相关的词："},{"type":"entry","text":"eclipse /ɪˈklɪps/ n. 日食，月食","headword":"eclipse"},{"type":"note","text":"搭配 lunar/solar eclipse 月/日食"},{"type":"text","text":"elliptic orbit椭圆轨道"},{"type":"entry","text":"equator /ɪˈkweɪtər/ n. 赤道","headword":"equator"},{"type":"note","text":"记忆 equat（=equate平均）+or→将地球进行等分→赤道"},{"type":"entry","text":"horizon /həˈraɪzn/ n. 地平线","headword":"horizon"},{"type":"note","text":"同根 horizontal a. 地平线的"},{"type":"entry","text":"orbit /ˈɔːrbɪt/ n. 轨道","headword":"orbit"},{"type":"note","text":"同根 orbital a. 轨道的"},{"type":"entry","text":"revolve /rɪˈvɔːlv/ vi. 旋转","headword":"revolve"},{"type":"note","text":"搭配 revolve around围绕…转动"},{"type":"entry","text":"spin /spɪn/ v. 旋转","headword":"spin"}]},{"number":40,"blocks":[{"type":"note","text":"同义 twirl v. 旋转"},{"type":"text","text":"其他天体星系常见词："},{"type":"text","text":"astronomical unit天文单位"},{"type":"entry","text":"astronomy /əˈstrɑːnəmi/ n. 天文学","headword":"astronomy"},{"type":"note","text":"同根 astronomical a. 天文学的"},{"type":"entry","text":"aureole /ˈɔːrioʊl/ n. 晕（日光或月光通过云层中冰晶经折射而形成","headword":"aureole"},{"type":"text","text":"的光环）"},{"type":"text","text":"Big Bang 宇宙大爆炸"},{"type":"text","text":"black mole 黑子"},{"type":"entry","text":"celestial /səˈlestʃl/ a. 天体的","headword":"celestial"},{"type":"note","text":"搭配 celestial body 天体"},{"type":"entry","text":"constellation /ˌkɑːnstəˈleɪʃn/ n. 星座","headword":"constellation"},{"type":"entry","text":"cosmos /ˈkɑːzmoʊs/ n. 宇宙","headword":"cosmos"},{"type":"note","text":"同义 universe n. 宇宙"},{"type":"entry","text":"galaxy /ˈɡæləksi/ n. 星系；银河系","headword":"galaxy"},{"type":"note","text":"同义 Milky Way 银河"},{"type":"entry","text":"intergalactic /ˌɪntərɡəˈlæktɪk/ a. 星系间的","headword":"intergalactic"},{"type":"note","text":"同根 galactic a. 银河的"},{"type":"entry","text":"interstellar /ˌɪntərˈstelər/ a. 星际的","headword":"interstellar"},{"type":"note","text":"同根 stellar a. 恒星的，星球的"},{"type":"entry","text":"lunar /ˈluːnər/ a. 月亮的","headword":"lunar"},{"type":"note","text":"搭配 lunar calendar 农历"},{"type":"entry","text":"meteorite /ˈmiːtiəraɪt/ n. 陨石","headword":"meteorite"},{"type":"note","text":"搭配 meteorite impact 陨石撞击"},{"type":"entry","text":"nebula /ˈnebjələ/ n. 星云","headword":"nebula"},{"type":"note","text":"同根 nebular a. 星云的，星云状的"}]},{"number":41,"blocks":[{"type":"text","text":"outer space 外太空"},{"type":"text","text":"planetary system 行星系"},{"type":"entry","text":"solar /ˈsoʊlər/ a. 太阳的","headword":"solar"},{"type":"note","text":"搭配 solar system 太阳系"},{"type":"text","text":"solar radiation 太阳辐射"},{"type":"text","text":"space station 太空站"},{"type":"text","text":"star cluster 星团"},{"type":"text","text":"sun’s rays 太阳光"},{"type":"entry","text":"twinkle /ˈtwɪŋkl/ vi. 闪烁","headword":"twinkle"},{"type":"note","text":"记忆 twinkle, twinkle, little star 一闪一闪小星星"},{"type":"entry","text":"wormhole /ˈwɜːrmhoʊl/ n. 虫洞","headword":"wormhole"}]}]}